# ⚠️ CRITICAL: Never commit files containing secrets
# These files should NEVER be committed - they contain sensitive credentials
# Including: API keys, database passwords, Razorpay keys, Firebase keys, etc.
# If accidentally committed, rotate all keys immediately!

